          (suggested by wiawkph@dutrun.tudelft.nl).
        (\leftdisplays): use it.
        * eplain.texinfo (Displays): document it.

        * eplain.tex (\@ddisplaytest): new macro to find an \eqdef in a
          display.
        (displaysetup): call it.

